                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Truly "The book that should have been in the box"</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
